# External / user skills live here.
#
# Skills in this folder are discovered AFTER the built-in skills in
# `mossy/skills/`, so a skill here with the same `name:` as an internal one
# overrides it (last-directory-wins). Drop a `<name>/SKILL.md` folder in here
# to add or override a skill without touching the package.
#
# This `.keep` file only exists so the otherwise-empty folder is tracked by git.
